@startuml
title Gambar 5.20 Sequence Diagram Backup Data

actor Admin
participant "Backup Page" as BackupPage
participant "Backup API" as BackupAPI
database Database
collections Storage

Admin -> BackupPage: Memilih aksi backup/export/import
BackupPage -> BackupAPI: Request proses backup
BackupAPI -> Database: Mengambil atau mengimpor data
Database --> BackupAPI: Data hasil proses
BackupAPI -> Storage: Menyimpan atau membaca file backup
Storage --> BackupAPI: Informasi file backup
BackupAPI --> BackupPage: Respons hasil proses
BackupPage --> Admin: Menampilkan status backup

@enduml
